{"type": "article", "id": 25256, "title": "看图：这里是过去那个周末发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。", "date": "2016-04-11T12:42:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021030566NkC4QwtPrKjVIF9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、印度寺庙大火</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103044ldBXYsap6I1k49Zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">印度寺庙大火的伤员在当地一间医院内。4 月 10 日凌晨，印度西南喀拉拉邦（Kerala）一间印度教寺庙发生火灾，已造成 100 多人死亡、350 人受伤。<b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、雅典民众游行</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021030455QnxDq07ZV4aHjAk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">barcroftmedia/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">希腊雅典，民众组织游行，抗议紧缩政策与高失业率。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><b style=\"line-height: 1.25;\">3、美国总统竞选</b><br></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103045r4cX9WnxFMSHT3sA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在罗切斯特的一场竞选活动中，一个手上带着刺青的人为共和党总统候选人特朗普录像。</p>\n<p><b>4、希腊边境</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103045N1ADUaRkIpP0bZqS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">希腊伊多梅尼（Idomeni）一处临时营地，一位妇女牵着孩子的手在浓雾中行走。</p>\n<p><b>5、撒哈拉沙漠马拉松</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103046SsXPyxZN8kpiQKJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">JEAN-PHILIPPE KSIAZEK/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一位参加第 31 届撒哈拉沙漠马拉松（Marathon des Sables）的选手。这一赛事也被称作是“地狱马拉松”，选手们需要在炙热的撒哈拉大沙漠腹地，跑完 257 千米的赛程。</p>\n<p><b>6、叙利亚街头</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103046L5nx7CJPsS0bz1I8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">AMER ALMOHIBANY/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在首都大马士革的郊区，孩子带着气球穿过严重损毁的房屋。</p>\n<h2>聚焦上海时装周：</h2>\n<p><b>1、开幕式现场</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103047jPgflFVYO7d2asT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210304724WAT9uiV0DlXqEr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103048gi0MJ9jSCdcYye5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021030489ds3KbPmT0aSg18U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">开幕式上身着 LANYU 服饰的模特。<br></p>\n<p><b>2、品牌秀场</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103049D7clQRWJ2gjonsKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210304971om36rJi4CvBKQp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021030502kzya8qDnTSVRjIH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103050I2JRBmjWn7VboFAY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">模特在秀场上展示服装品牌作品。</p>\n<p><b>3、时尚街拍</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103050PQ5XRVlN8edSsDjq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103051WUboTDHMKy7mYLui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103051Kj2hVvf30IUcSQ4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103052uGzUpdQwJqayNC5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103052OoZ8TmIpkl5zej71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103053dzEQoUkPKIxsT2MR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103053VhYkNEZqvUfmwnxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">时装周开幕以来，各类“潮人”出现在上海街头。</p>\n<h2 class=\"\">除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p><b>1、消失的边境</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103054TBVn4b3SEKMhDuNR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">墨西哥墨西卡利（Mexicali），志愿者参加一项名为“消除边界”（Borrando la Frontera）的艺术活动，将美国和墨西哥之间的隔离墙粉刷成天空蓝，制造出墙体消失的错觉。<br></p>\n<p><b>2、西班牙舞蹈月</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103054XlOodWMaLSfj4ygn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">ANDER GILLENEA/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">西班牙圣塞瓦斯蒂安（San Sebastian），一名舞者在 La Concha 海湾跳舞，庆祝“舞蹈月”到来。<br></p>\n<p><b>3、里约海滩</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103055w85gWO2P9THtZ1cF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一名男子在巴西里约热内卢的 Recreio dos Bandeirantes 海滩上奔跑。</p>\n<p><b>4、盛开的紫荆花</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103055JzKC6XhiRanSt8PQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">柳叶/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>广西壮族自治区柳州市，车辆从开满紫荆花的柳州市学院路经过。</p>\n\n"}